  "prompt": "Which is the best app to make anonymous call online?",
  "response": "There are several apps that offer anonymous calling services. Some popular options include:\n\n1. Burner\n- Creates temporary phone numbers\n- Available on iOS and Android\n- Good for privacy and temporary communication\n\n2. TextNow\n- Free anonymous calling and texting\n- Provides a virtual phone number\n- Web and mobile app options\n\n3. Google Voice\n- Offers a secondary phone number\n- Free calls within the US and Canada\n- Provides call screening and blocking features\n\n4. Hushed\n- Temporary and disposable phone numbers\n- Multiple country options\n- Strong privacy features\n\n5. Dingtone\n- Free calling and texting\n- WiFi-based calls\n- Anonymous number creation\n\nEach app has different features and pricing, so the \"best\" depends on your specific needs. Consider factors like:\n- Cost\n- Call quality\n- Geographic availability\n- Privacy features\n- Ease of use\n\nI recommend comparing their current features and reviews to choose the most suitable option for your requirements.",
